\">87</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">423</biblScope></bibl>. (Since the <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Subst.\">Subst.</a></pos> is implied for <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> in <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">πολυτρήρων, τ.</foreign> is perh. always a <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Subst.\">Subst.</a></pos>, name of the genus, and <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τ. πελειάδες</foreign> is to be compared with <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἴρηξ κίρκος, σῦς κάπρος,</foreign> etc.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}